{{Databox|en=Nafusi language}}'''Tanfusit''' niɣd '''mazoɣ''' tga tutlayt li sawaln Imaziɣn n Drar n nfusn ɣ Libya. Adrar n infusn illa ɣ tamurt n [[libya]], '''Tanfusit''' tga ula yat tulayt ɣ tutlayin n imaziɣn lli ukan sul idrn, waxxa tbid tanbaṭ n libya ɣ ddu ifasn l-qddafi bac ast tmḍl. 
Art sawaln uggar n 200 000 n umdan. Tangalt (ISO 639-3) ns igat: jbn. tawjan ns Camitu-simitik z tutlayin tifrusyatin niɣd [[Tutlayin tifrusyawiyin]]. Mck abdda tsmun id bu icnubcn n tutlayt mas tga z tutlayin n [[tuns]]. Mac nttat naḥayat disnt.

==Adrar n infusn==
Adrar n infusn iga yan ɣ idrarn n tamurt n [[libya]] lli walan [[Imaziɣn|imaziΓn]] , ig yan ugadir lli bdda yakkan ixatarn n imaziɣn, inin waεrabn is iga yan udrar lli fllasn iqn. Acku midn ns gan irgazn baḥra cqqanin.

==Tirra n tanfusit== 
infusitn ar taran tamaziɣt ns iskkiln tifinaɣ d iskkiln iramiyn (zund win taεrabt (Ẓr tawalt ɣid: [http://www.tawalt.com/ Tawalt]) Mac aras zmmuẓzuln z mad issufɣ [[AATT]] niɣd ('''Asinag Ageldan Tussna Tamaziɣt'''. s [[tifinaɣ]] "'''ⴰⵙⵉⵏⴰⴳ ⴰⴳⵍⴷⴰⵏ ⵏ ⵜⵓⵙⵙⵏⴰ ⵜⴰⵎⴰⵣⵉⵖⵜ'''") n tamurt n [[Amṛṛuk|umṛṛuk]] iskkiln imaynutn n [[tifinaɣ]].
